{
  "texts": [
    "Biases in LLM predictions Recent work has revealed various biases in the predictions of LLMs.",
    "Wang et al. (2023a) showed that models exhibit positional bias when presented with several texts for evaluation and ranking.",
    "Pezeshkpour and Hruschka (2023) and Zheng et al. (2024) exposed a similar bias in multi-choice QA.",
    "Si et al. (2023) studied inductive biases in in-context learning.",
    "Complimentary to these works, we study label bias and seek to improve its evaluation and mitigation."
  ]
}